## 🧠 Built Using Streamlit in Snowflake

This application is deployed using **Streamlit in Snowflake**, enabling:

* ⚡ Real-time data interaction directly within the data cloud
* 🔐 Secure access using role-based authentication
* 🚀 Zero infrastructure management (fully managed by Snowflake)
* 🔄 Seamless integration with Snowpark and database layers

Streamlit allows rapid development of interactive data apps, while Snowflake provides scalable compute and storage — eliminating the need for external backend systems. ([DataCamp][1])

